Comment: The original description is based on &quot;ein einziges Männchen&quot; from &quot;Buchara&quot; (today 
<collectingCountry id="F3207609C048ED44BBA3FA269C3F2020" box="[463,607,1509,1537]" name="Uzbekistan" pageId="3" pageNumber="250">Uzbekistan</collectingCountry>
