<bibRefCitation id="EFA64B68C048ED44BE47FA269AA72020" author="KOCH C" box="[1067,1223,1509,1537]" pageId="3" pageNumber="250" pagination="45 - 52" refId="ref9201" refString="KOCH C. (1944): Uber neue und wenig bekannte palaarktische Paederinae (Col. Staph.). - Casopis Ceske Spolecnosti Entomologicke 41: 45 - 52." type="journal article" year="1944">KOCH 1944</bibRefCitation>
), which is currently housed in the NHMB. The species is known only from the 
<typeStatus id="548C883BC048ED44BE0EF9CF9AF92009" box="[1122,1177,1548,1576]" pageId="3" pageNumber="250">type</typeStatus>
locality (
<figureCitation id="130C2A1CC048ED44BF79F9CF9E91206F" captionStart="Map 1" captionStartId="5.[226,283,1941,1966]" captionTargetBox="[226,1359,1001,1916]" captionTargetId="figure-251@5.[226,1359,1390,1916]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Map 1: Type localities of Lathrobium bucharense KOCH (triangle) and L. bananum nov.sp. (circle)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6518393" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6518393/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="250">Map 1</figureCitation>
